(12,	227,	'tim',	'',	'',	'',	'2019-05-20 06:56:04',	'2019-05-20 06:56:04',	'I am a graphic designer. I loved this course as well. My instructor was very helpful for leaning UI/UX design. This course made me a big fan of UI/UX design and Udemy as well. Its gave me a new hopes in my creative career.',	0,	'approved',	'',	'tutor_course_rating',	0,	0),
(13,	227,	'jose',	'',	'',	'',	'2019-05-20 06:57:02',	'2019-05-20 06:57:02',	'Just completed the course:) Thank you so much, it was easy to follow and a big step, onwards and upwards, I also got your course on dreamweaver and I\\\'m looking forward to getting stuck in. I\\\'m sure will be as helpful and laid back as the last, really happy thank you.',	0,	'approved',	'',	'tutor_course_rating',	0,	0),
