(15,	248,	'jose',	'',	'',	'',	'2019-05-22 06:26:29',	'2019-05-22 06:26:29',	'Great course. Well structured, paced and I feel far more confident using this software now then I did back in school when I was learning. And the guy doing the voice over really is great at what he does. I will probably do the course again and look at what other courses this instructor provides. Great quality and well worth the cost.',	0,	'approved',	'',	'tutor_course_rating',	0,	0),
